Class Coffee

java.lang.Object
com.example.rucafe.Coffee
All Implemented Interfaces:
Customizable, MenuItem
public class Coffee extends Object implements Customizable, MenuItem
Coffee Class is a class that defines the properties that comes with an instance of a coffee and the corresponding methods that go with it.
